  "questions": [
    {
      "text": "A 45-year-old patient presents with a small, flat, reddish-brown lesion on the palm of their hand. The lesion is non-palpable and measures approximately 5 mm in diameter. What is the most likely description of this lesion?",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": 0,
          "text": "Papule"
        },
        {
          "id": 1,
          "text": "Plaque"
        },
        {
          "id": 2,
          "text": "Macule"
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "text": "Bulla"
        }
      ],
      "correct_choice_id": 2,
      "solution": "<p><strong>Correct Answer: C) Macule</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Explanation:</strong><br />\nA <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"dc2eebe088169277719115b8c50b0c\">macule</span> is a flat, non-raised <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"d5e7bb15851692777191b39417c26a\">lesion</span> less than 1 cm in <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"afb15e4a331692777186e495b370a1\">diameter</span> characterized by a change in skin colour or pigmentation.</p>\n\n<div style=\"text-align:center\">\n<figure class=\"caption_element\" style=\"display:inline-block\"><img alt=\"\" data-author=\"CNX OpenStax,\" data-hash=\"\" data-license=\"CC BY 4.0\" data-source=\"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:OSC_Microbio_21_01_LesionLine.jpg\" data-tags=\"\" height=\"2081\" src=\"https://image.prepladder.com/content/GEabq4gHrcyOLNOsHLMS1733921452.png\" width=\"3765\" />\n<figcaption>{{caption_text}}</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n<table align=\"center\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; width:620px\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-color:#000000; border-style:solid; border-width:1px; vertical-align:top; width:350px\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Skin Lesions <1 cm</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-color:#000000; border-style:solid; border-width:1px; vertical-align:top; width:350px\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Skin Lesions >1 cm</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-color:#000000; border-style:solid; border-width:1px; vertical-align:top; width:350px\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Macule:</strong> Flat, non-raised lesion <strong>(Option C)</strong></p>\n\n\t\t\t<p> </p>\n\n\t\t\t<p>  </p>\n\n\t\t\t<div style=\"text-align:center\">\n\t\t\t<figure class=\"caption_element\" style=\"display:inline-block\"><img alt=\"\" data-author=\"Sarahrosenau \" data-hash=\"\" data-license=\"CC BY SA 2.0\" data-source=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tinea_versicolor\" data-tags=\"\" height=\"1851\" src=\"https://image.prepladder.com/content/zGlYlIdyPavGx5kFABmJ1733921480.png\" width=\"3870\" />\n\t\t\t<figcaption>{{caption_text}}</figcaption>\n\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-color:#000000; border-style:solid; border-width:1px; vertical-align:top; width:350px\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Patch:</strong> Flat, non-raised lesion</p>\n\n\t\t\t<p> </p>\n\n\t\t\t<p>  </p>\n\n\t\t\t<div style=\"text-align:center\">\n\t\t\t<figure class=\"caption_element\" style=\"display:inline-block\"><img alt=\"\" data-author=\"Madhero88,\" data-hash=\"\" data-license=\"CC BY-SA 4.0\" data-source=\"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Macule_and_Patch.svg\" data-tags=\"\" height=\"2947\" src=\"https://image.prepladder.com/content/oiAT5rSvBD2fKWSBBzc01733921948.png\" width=\"4050\" />\n\t\t\t<figcaption>{{caption_text}}</figcaption>\n\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Papule:</strong> Raised, circumscribed, solid <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"d5e7bb15851692777191b39417c26a\">lesion</span> <strong>(Option A ruled out)</strong> < 1cm</p>\n\n\t\t\t<p> </p>\n\n\t\t\t<p>   </p>\n\n\t\t\t<div style=\"text-align:center\">\n\t\t\t<figure class=\"caption_element\" style=\"display:inline-block\"><img alt=\"\" data-author=\"Madhero88,\" data-hash=\"\" data-license=\"CC BY-SA 3.0\" data-source=\"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Papule_and_Plaque.svg\" data-tags=\"\" height=\"2771\" src=\"https://image.prepladder.com/content/KiYTHzyRRTY7uVrHyIla1733921574.png\" width=\"3859\" />\n\t\t\t<figcaption>{{caption_text}}</figcaption>\n\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Plaque: </strong>Elevated <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"89aa50eac91692777184c8f668d2cf\">circumscribed</span> lesion</p>\n\n\t\t\t<p><strong>(Option B ruled out) </strong>> 1cm</p>\n\n\t\t\t<p>  </p>\n\n\t\t\t<div style=\"text-align:center\">\n\t\t\t<figure class=\"caption_element\" style=\"display:inline-block\"><img alt=\"\" data-author=\"Madhero88,\" data-hash=\"\" data-license=\"CC BY-SA 3.0\" data-source=\"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Papule_and_Plaque.svg\" data-tags=\"\" height=\"2771\" src=\"https://image.prepladder.com/content/anRHYeYHrvHQ0bajPfYA1733921579.png\" width=\"3859\" />\n\t\t\t<figcaption>{{caption_text}}</figcaption>\n\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Vesicle:</strong> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"89aa50eac91692777184c8f668d2cf\">Circumscribed</span> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"a1f256489a16927771870ddd296574\">elevation</span> less than < 1cm in <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"afb15e4a331692777186e495b370a1\">diameter</span> that contains fluid (clear, <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"3963a2e0fa169277719874304f5705\">serous</span> or haemorrhagic) and is often grouped</p>\n\n\t\t\t<div style=\"text-align:center\">\n\t\t\t<figure class=\"caption_element\" style=\"display:inline-block\"><img alt=\"\" data-author=\"gentgeen\" data-hash=\"\" data-license=\"CC BY-SA 3.0\" data-source=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shingles\" data-tags=\"\" height=\"3732\" src=\"https://image.prepladder.com/content/YWhHJuJJEI9U7GweLaaD1733921646.png\" width=\"3954\" />\n\t\t\t<figcaption>{{caption_text}}</figcaption>\n\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t<p> </p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Bullae:</strong> Bullae are more than > 1cm in <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"afb15e4a331692777186e495b370a1\">diameter</span> <strong>(Option D ruled out).</strong></p>\n\n\t\t\t<p> </p>\n\n\t\t\t<div style=\"text-align:center\">\n\t\t\t<figure class=\"caption_element\" style=\"display:inline-block\"><img alt=\"\" data-author=\"Novakreo,\" data-hash=\"\" data-license=\"CC BY-SA 3.0\" data-source=\"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Blister.jpg\" data-tags=\"\" height=\"3517\" src=\"https://image.prepladder.com/content/qZ3Fe12k9Dw8zA5ZudPJ1733921630.png\" width=\"4054\" />\n\t\t\t<figcaption>{{caption_text}}</figcaption>\n\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Petechiae:</strong> Punctate haemorrhagic spot, approximately 1–2 mm in diameter.</p>\n\n\t\t\t<div style=\"text-align:center\">\n\t\t\t<figure class=\"caption_element\" style=\"display:inline-block\"><img alt=\"\" data-author=\"Candelli, Marcello & Rossi, Elena & Valletta, Federico & De Stefano, Valerio & Franceschi, Francesco.\" data-hash=\"\" data-license=\"NA\" data-source=\"https://www.researchgate.net/figure/Petechiae-on-the-patients-right-leg-in-the-Emergency-Room-Colour-figure-can-be-viewed_fig1_351284881\" data-tags=\"\" height=\"870\" src=\"https://image.prepladder.com/content/rwMwaFjO5OQq3vgpAUEP1733921663.png\" width=\"521\" />\n\t\t\t<figcaption>{{caption_text}}</figcaption>\n\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t<p> </p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Ecchymoses:</strong> A <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"ebad8eb48c1692777191b5de5d04a1\">macular</span> area of haemorrhage more than 1cm (bruise) in diameter.</p>\n\n\t\t\t<div style=\"text-align:center\">\n\t\t\t<figure class=\"caption_element\" style=\"display:inline-block\"><img alt=\"\" data-author=\"Leonardo M. Lustosa, \" data-hash=\"\" data-license=\"CC BY-SA 4.0\" data-source=\"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Kirmisson%27s_and_pucker_sign.jpg\" data-tags=\"\" height=\"683\" src=\"https://image.prepladder.com/content/6qaFtiyeXinXOvJL1QJv1733921672.png\" width=\"888\" />\n\t\t\t<figcaption>{{caption_text}}</figcaption>\n\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t<p> </p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\"><strong>Purpura: </strong>Haemorrhagic spots more than 3mm but less than 1cm caused by <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"41e858bf2816927771836d46c619b9\">bleeding</span> underneath the skin</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\"> </td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>",
